---
title: Mexican Beef Supper Nachos with Avocado
description: These saucy supper nachos are jam-packed with a secret veggie component: grated zucchini! And how about that - you can make your own tortilla chips at home! And these chips are the perfect utensil to scoop up all the beefy deliciousness.
